scene.message:
Himeno: U-um...{nl}
{ctl0f:1}, you're going{nl}
to Mikage Hospital, right...?{waitkey}{ret}

{color:3}Yuko Himeno{nl}
Maki's friend. A devoted girl{nl}
working part-time to help{nl}
support her family.{waitkey}{ret}

Himeno: Um, sorry to ask,{wait_fr:32}{nl}
but could you tell Sonomura{nl}
I'll return the book I{waitkey}{nl}
borrowed next time I visit?{nl}
{ctl0e:1}{ret}

Himeno: U-um...{nl}
thank you.{nl}
Sorry to trouble you...{waitkey}{ret}

Himeno: U-um... well...{nl}
I asked something weird...{nl}
sorry, just forget it...!{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: {ctl0f:1}!{nl}
Don't be such a{nl}
cheapskate!{waitkey}{ret}

Himeno: Um, that book,{nl}
it was so good I'm{nl}
reading it again...{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Whoa, that's deep!{nl}
You read stuff like that,{nl}
Sonomura...{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: If you like it that{nl}
much, why not just buy{nl}
your own copy?{waitkey}{ret}

Himeno: U-um... it's a bit{nl}
pricey, I can't afford it...{wait_fr:48}{nl}
And I want to buy my brother{waitkey}new clothes too...{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: Nanjo, you idiot!{nl}
She works part-time to{nl}
help her family!{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Well, we're in a{nl}
hurry, so!{nl}
We'll be sure to tell her!{waitkey}{ret}

Himeno: U-um...{nl}
did you tell Sonomura,{nl}
I wonder...{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: Sorry, not yet.{nl}
But we'll go soon.{waitkey}{nl}
...Hey, {ctl0f:1}!{nl}
Let's get to the hospital!{waitkey}{ret}
